Features
  - Add '.mt-translate' to static divs that won't change (header/etc)
  - Add '.mt-ignore' to those you want to ignore
  - Easily change library

Translation:
 - Add an input with "#mt-input"
 - Add another input with "#mt-output"
 - run mt_watch(library,in,out) and it will translate them whenever input changes





